OL,4,CEngland Schoolboys footballer at car
OL,5,Cmeet
OL,7,FThe court heard Mr Harding was a
OL,8,Ftalented footballer and had been a
OL,9,Fcoach and mentor to hundreds of
OL,10,Fchildren in his local area. His mother
OL,11,Fsaid he was excited to attend his
OL,12,Ffirst car meet.
OL,14,FMore than 20 members of his family
OL,15,Fwere in court for the hearing while
OL,16,FHodgson's parents and brother sat on
OL,17,Fthe opposite side of the public
OL,18,Fgallery.
OL,20,FHodgson, from Morley in Leeds, was
OL,21,Fjailed for eight years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
