OL,3,CDriver jailed for killing former
OL,4,CEngland Schoolboys footballer at car
OL,5,Cmeet
OL,7,FSentencing him, Judge Neil Flewitt
OL,8,Fsaid: "You have an entrenched and
OL,9,Fcavalier attitude to driving at speed.
OL,11,F"You made a deliberate decision to
OL,12,Fignore the rules of the road and you
OL,13,Fshowed complete disregard for the risk
OL,14,Fof danger to others.
OL,16,F"You travelled at speeds far in excess
OL,17,Fof the speed limit."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
