OL,7,FPolice also found videos on Hodgson's
OL,8,Fphone showing his car being driven on
OL,9,Fthe motorway in the weeks before the
OL,10,Fcrash at speeds of more than 150mph.
OL,12,FThe court heard he was convicted in
OL,13,F2023 of five offences of failing to
OL,14,Fprovide the identification of the
OL,15,Fdriver in the clips.
OL,17,FMartyn Walsh, defending Hodgson, said:
OL,18,F"Through me he wishes to apologise and
OL,19,Fsay sorry for what happened on that
OL,20,Fnight."
